{"article_id":"EDbuWTZrnmRW4GpY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Friday threatened to close the southern border `` entirely ''","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"if he does not get the funding","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"he needs","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"for his border wall ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that it would be a `` profit-making operation '' to do so .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"He also said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"the U.S. would be cutting off `` all aid '' to three Central American countries","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"-- Honduras , Guatemala and El Salvador --","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"are the source of immigrant caravans","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"coming to the U.S .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"`` We build a wall","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"or we close the southern border , ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"he said in a series of Friday morning tweets .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"We will be forced to close the Southern Border entirely","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"if the Obstructionist Democrats do not give us the money","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"to finish the Wall","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"& also change the ridiculous immigration laws","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"that our Country is saddled with .","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"Hard to believe","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"there was a Congress & President","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"who would approve !","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"December 28 , 2018 ....","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"The United States looses soooo much money on Trade with Mexico under NAFTA , over 75 Billion Dollars a year","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"( not including Drug Money","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"which would be many times that amount ) ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"that I would consider closing the Southern Border a \" profit making operation. \"","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"We build a Wall or .....","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"December 28 , 2018 ..... close the Southern Border .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Bring our car industry back into the United States","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"where it belongs .","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"Go back to pre-NAFTA ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"before so many of our companies and jobs were so foolishly sent to Mexico .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Either we build","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"( finish )","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"the Wall","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"or we close the Border ......","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"December 28 , 2018 .....","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Honduras , Guatemala and El Salvador are doing nothing for the United States","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"but taking our money .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Word is that a new Caravan is forming in Honduras","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and they are doing nothing about it .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"We will be cutting off all aid to these 3 countries -","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"taking advantage of U.S. for years !","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"December 28 , 2018","depth":3},{"id":55,"text":"Acting Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney reiterated to reporters","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"that Mr. Trump would be willing to shut down the border ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"saying `` yes ''","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"when asked","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"if the president meant what he said in his tweets .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"CBS has estimated","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"that closing the southern border would cost up to $ 1 billion a day .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"Still ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"as the partial government shutdown enters day seven ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders told `` CBS This Morning '' Friday","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that Mr. Trump is `` willing to negotiate '' with Democrats on the $ 5 billion","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"he is requesting","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to fund the wall .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Sanders blasted Democrats for the standoff","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that is now expected to keep roughly 800,000 federal workers from receiving paychecks into the New Year ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"claiming","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"they have `` left the table altogether ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"but not offering details on what the president might be willing to agree to .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"`` I 'm not going to negotiate in the press ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"but the president has been willing to negotiate on this point","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"and the Democrats have not been willing to do anything , ''","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"`` It 's a very sad day","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"when we ca n't get Democrats to even show up for work","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"and sit down with us","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and have these conversations","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and try to help make real solutions","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"and get something done . ''","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Mulvaney also said","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"negotiations have completely shut down ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"and repeated Sanders ' argument","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"that Democrats were more interested in protecting Nancy Pelosi 's speakership than the border .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Because of this ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"they did not expect anything s